<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Domus Nawak | O Futuro da Web</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #1A0B2E; /* Roxo Profundo */
            color: white;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            font-family: sans-serif;
        }
        .gradient-text {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00D1FF, #FF8A00);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        .glass {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .floating {
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
            100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
        }
        .blob {
            position: absolute;
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            background: #FF8A00;
            filter: blur(80px);
            opacity: 0.2;
            z-index: -1;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="blob top-10 left-10"></div>
    <div class="blob bottom-10 right-10" style="background: #00D1FF;"></div>

    <nav class="flex justify-between items-center p-6 glass sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tighter">
            DOMUS <span class="text-[#FF8A00]">NAWAK</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-x-8 hidden md:flex">
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-[#00D1FF] transition">Editor</a>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-[#00D1FF] transition">Hospedagem</a>
            <a href="#" class="hover:text-[#00D1FF] transition">Domínios</a>
        </div>
        <button class="bg-[#00D1FF] text-[#1A0B2E] px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-bold hover:scale-105 transition">
            Começar Grátis
        </button>
    </nav>

    <section class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[80vh] text-center px-4">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-black mb-6 floating">
            Crie sites que <br><span class="gradient-text">arrasão o mundo.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-xl max-w-2xl mb-10">
            A fusão perfeita entre a liberdade do código e o poder da hospedagem profissional. 
            Simples, rápido e com a estética que seu projeto merece.
        </p>
        
        <div class="glass p-2 rounded-2xl flex w-full max-w-xl items-center">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Busque seu domínio grátis..." class="bg-transparent flex-grow p-4 outline-none text-white">
            <button class="bg-[#FF8A00] p-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-orange-600 transition">
                <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
            </button>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500 italic">Domínios .nawak grátis para sempre.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="p-10 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl hover:border-[#00D1FF] transition group">
            <i class="fas fa-code text-4xl text-[#00D1FF] mb-4"></i>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">IDE Ultra-Rápida</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Edite seu código com preview em tempo real e IA integrada.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl hover:border-[#FF8A00] transition group">
            <i class="fas fa-server text-4xl text-[#FF8A00] mb-4"></i>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Hospedagem Edge</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Seu site online em segundos com a velocidade da luz.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl hover:border-[#00D1FF] transition group">
            <i class="fas fa-rocket text-4xl text-[#00D1FF] mb-4"></i>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Deploy em 1 Click</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400">Integração nativa com GitHub e Vercel para lançamentos rápidos.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
